<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢٥٣٣ - <span class="c4">[٢٩]</span> <span class="c2">(ابن عباس)</span> قوله: <span class="c2">(<span class="c3">{وَتَزَوَّدُوا فَإِنَّ خَيْرَ الزَّادِ التَّقْوَى}</span>)</span> أي:<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>